00:13:07.880 --> 00:13:09.920 align:middle line:90%
has ever experienced.

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:13.280 align:middle line:84%
And invited me to go
with him to his tribal,

00:13:13.280 --> 00:13:17.090 align:middle line:84%
an ancient tribal
location to pray rain.

00:13:17.090 --> 00:13:21.000 align:middle line:84%
And this is key, to pray
rain, not pray for rain.

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.550 align:middle line:84%
Well, I went out
with an expectation

00:13:22.550 --> 00:13:25.010 align:middle line:84%
that I would see a lot
of dancing and movement

00:13:25.010 --> 00:13:26.800 align:middle line:90%
and chanting.

00:13:26.800 --> 00:13:30.380 align:middle line:84%
And a little bit to
my disappointment,

00:13:30.380 --> 00:13:33.860 align:middle line:84%
I stood off and watched this
gentleman walk to a tribal spot

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:37.610 align:middle line:84%
where his family done it for
thousands of generations.

00:13:37.610 --> 00:13:40.730 align:middle line:84%
He took off his shoes,
walked into his stone circle,

00:13:40.730 --> 00:13:43.040 align:middle line:84%
and I saw very little outward
expression of the prayer.

00:13:43.040 --> 00:13:45.290 align:middle line:84%
And then he came back and
he said, well, I'm finished.

00:13:45.290 --> 00:13:46.880 align:middle line:90%
Let's go get a bite to eat.

00:13:46.880 --> 00:13:48.860 align:middle line:84%
And I said, well,
what about the prayer?

00:13:48.860 --> 00:13:50.000 align:middle line:90%
And he says, I just did it.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.400 align:middle line:90%
And I said, well, what happened?

00:13:51.400 --> 00:13:53.150 align:middle line:84%
I thought you were
going to pray for rain.

00:13:53.150 --> 00:13:54.200 align:middle line:90%
And he said, no.

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:56.957 align:middle line:84%
If I pray for rain, I'm
acknowledging it doesn't exist

00:13:56.957 --> 00:13:58.040 align:middle line:90%
and it will never happen--

00:13:58.040 --> 00:14:01.040 align:middle line:84%
>> So the universe
answers, OK, you want rain?

00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:02.060 align:middle line:90%
We don't have rain here.

00:14:02.060 --> 00:14:03.860 align:middle line:84%
>> You're just
saying pray for rain.

00:14:03.860 --> 00:14:07.740 align:middle line:84%
He said, I prayed rain and what
