00:14:07.740 --> 00:14:10.610 align:middle line:84%
and I had the thoughts,
feelings, and emotions of what

00:14:10.610 --> 00:14:13.910 align:middle line:84%
it feels like to feel the
mud ooze between my toes

00:14:13.910 --> 00:14:15.890 align:middle line:84%
during the rainstorm
in my village.

00:14:15.890 --> 00:14:18.860 align:middle line:84%
He said, I smelled the smell
of the water coming off

00:14:18.860 --> 00:14:20.390 align:middle line:90%
the pueblo walls.

00:14:20.390 --> 00:14:23.000 align:middle line:84%
I felt what it feels like to
walk through fields of corn

00:14:23.000 --> 00:14:25.910 align:middle line:84%
up to my chest because
the rain is so plentiful.

00:14:25.910 --> 00:14:28.130 align:middle line:90%
And doing that, I created--

00:14:28.130 --> 00:14:30.410 align:middle line:84%
somewhere in creation--
I just created rain.

00:14:30.410 --> 00:14:32.150 align:middle line:90%
Maybe not here, somewhere.

00:14:32.150 --> 00:14:36.380 align:middle line:84%
Now, my prayer becomes a prayer
of thanks for what I've created

00:14:36.380 --> 00:14:38.225 align:middle line:84%
and I know that it
will come to pass.

00:14:38.225 --> 00:14:40.350 align:middle line:84%
Well, the next day, we
