00:14:42.493 --> 00:14:43.910 align:middle line:84%
than we knew what
to do with and I

00:14:43.910 --> 00:14:46.040 align:middle line:84%
called him and I said, how
come we've got so much rain?

00:14:46.040 --> 00:14:47.060 align:middle line:84%
And he said, well,
that's the part

00:14:47.060 --> 00:14:48.060 align:middle line:90%
I haven't got figured out yet.

00:14:48.060 --> 00:14:50.560 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, but see, we don't want
to pray for something for it

00:14:50.560 --> 00:14:51.650 align:middle line:90%
to happen somewhere else.

00:14:51.650 --> 00:14:52.820 align:middle line:90%
We want it to happen here.

00:14:52.820 --> 00:14:53.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:14:53.620 --> 00:14:56.005 align:middle line:84%
>> So where in his
prayer does he say,

00:14:56.005 --> 00:14:57.630 align:middle line:84%
please have it rain
here in New Mexico.

00:14:57.630 --> 00:14:58.790 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, it was.

00:14:58.790 --> 00:15:01.220 align:middle line:84%
It was in New Mexico
where we had that rain.

00:15:01.220 --> 00:15:02.960 align:middle line:90%
And this is the--

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:04.970 align:middle line:84%
the prayer, this
last mode of prayer

00:15:04.970 --> 00:15:08.310 align:middle line:84%
in feeling the outcome before it
ever happens, and in that way,

00:15:08.310 --> 00:15:10.910 align:middle line:84%
creating it, that's the
language to creation.

00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:13.220 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't promise that
it will come to pass,

00:15:13.220 --> 00:15:15.890 align:middle line:90%
it creates the possibility--

00:15:15.890 --> 00:15:19.760 align:middle line:84%
that's the seed-- now, our
prayer is a prayer of thanks,

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:23.090 align:middle line:84%
and our thanks is what
empowers that seed.

00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:26.000 align:middle line:84%
It gives it life so it
can last to come to pass.

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:28.252 align:middle line:84%
This is what we lost
1,700 years ago.

00:15:28.252 --> 00:15:29.710 align:middle line:84%
In our world, if
we do a prayer, it

00:15:29.710 --> 00:15:31.550 align:middle line:84%
doesn't happen immediately
in front of us.

00:15:31.550 --> 00:15:32.750 align:middle line:84%
We say it never
happened because--

00:15:32.750 --> 00:15:34.160 align:middle line:90%
>> Because God's not listening.

00:15:34.160 --> 00:15:35.990 align:middle line:84%
>> Right, because
that's our expectation.

00:15:35.990 --> 00:15:38.630 align:middle line:84%
The ancients knew beyond
the shadow of a doubt

00:15:38.630 --> 00:15:41.422 align:middle line:84%
that they are empowered
in this world to create.

00:15:41.422 --> 00:15:43.880 align:middle line:84%
And the moment they had that
thought, feeling, and emotion,

00:15:43.880 --> 00:15:46.910 align:middle line:84%
it has happened somewhere,
they trusted that.

00:15:46.910 --> 00:15:50.600 align:middle line:84%
And we don't trust that now
up until very recently anyway.

00:15:50.600 --> 00:15:52.310 align:middle line:84%
In trusting that,
they would simply

00:15:52.310 --> 00:15:55.760 align:middle line:84%
continue maybe for days
with prayers of thanks

00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:58.200 align:middle line:84%
because they trusted
it come to pass.

00:15:58.200 --> 00:15:59.870 align:middle line:90%
So now, back to your example.

00:15:59.870 --> 00:16:02.600 align:middle line:84%
I would give thanks for
the health and the vitality

00:16:02.600 --> 00:16:06.890 align:middle line:84%
of my child who
in this moment may

00:16:06.890 --> 00:16:09.800 align:middle line:84%
be projecting an illusion
of illness through a body.

00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:13.665 align:middle line:84%
And I know that the soul is new,
shiny, and intact as the day it

00:16:13.665 --> 00:16:16.040 align:middle line:84%
burst forth from the heart of
the creator into this world

00:16:16.040 --> 00:16:17.940 align:middle line:84%
and there is no
illness in the soul,

00:16:17.940 --> 00:16:21.420 align:middle line:84%
that that body is simply
mirroring a process of learning

00:16:21.420 --> 00:16:22.220 align:middle line:90%
and understanding.

00:16:22.220 --> 00:16:23.600 align:middle line:90%
And I trust that process.

00:16:23.600 --> 00:16:25.460 align:middle line:90%
I trust that with all my heart.

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:30.590 align:middle line:84%
And I asked, I give thanks
for the process and thanks

00:16:30.590 --> 00:16:33.237 align:middle line:84%
