playing out in front of me.

00:16:33.237 --> 00:16:34.820 align:middle line:84%
And that's very
different than saying,

00:16:34.820 --> 00:16:37.877 align:middle line:84%
please help me do
something I'm afraid of,

00:16:37.877 --> 00:16:39.585 align:middle line:84%
I don't understand
what's happening here.

00:16:39.585 --> 00:16:43.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Let's suppose the child dies,
