00:16:43.310 --> 00:16:46.130 align:middle line:84%
>> Through the science
of compassion and through

00:16:46.130 --> 00:16:48.500 align:middle line:84%
redefining our relationship
with that child,

00:16:48.500 --> 00:16:50.630 align:middle line:84%
with the creative
