00:17:02.570 --> 00:17:05.210 align:middle line:10%
according to ancient text,
we're in this world learning

00:17:05.210 --> 00:17:07.940 align:middle line:10%
to love on levels deeper than
even the angels in the heavens

00:17:07.940 --> 00:17:10.339 align:middle line:10%
have ever learned to love
because they've never

00:17:10.339 --> 00:17:13.118 align:middle line:10%
had to face what we're
facing here in this world.

00:17:13.118 --> 00:17:16.400 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, you say something
here in your book about

00:17:16.400 --> 00:17:18.980 align:middle line:90%
the dark knight of the soul.

00:17:18.980 --> 00:17:23.490 align:middle line:84%
