and your family, your job,

00:17:59.300 --> 00:18:01.070 align:middle line:84%
your house, your car,
everything is gone.

00:18:01.070 --> 00:18:03.920 align:middle line:84%
And in that moment, we're
pushed to the very edge

00:18:03.920 --> 00:18:07.940 align:middle line:84%
