digitally, and there's

00:18:18.260 --> 00:18:21.950 align:middle line:84%
a whole science behind
this, is that we're not

00:18:21.950 --> 00:18:24.680 align:middle line:84%
capable of having those
experiences, of losing health,

00:18:24.680 --> 00:18:26.640 align:middle line:84%
of losing finance, of
losing friends, and jobs,

00:18:26.640 --> 00:18:27.440 align:middle line:90%
and marriage.

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:32.600 align:middle line:84%
It cannot happen until we have
amassed every tool that is

00:18:32.600 --> 00:18:35.840 align:middle line:84%
