through that experience.

00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:38.420 align:middle line:84%
And the key is we never know
when it's going to happen.

00:18:38.420 --> 00:18:38.960 align:middle line:90%
If there are big neon sign--

00:18:38.960 --> 00:18:39.980 align:middle line:90%
>> But many people--

00:18:39.980 --> 00:18:42.275 align:middle line:84%
>> --it would be
different, but there's not.

00:18:42.275 --> 00:18:45.980 align:middle line:90%
>> Many people keep everything.

00:18:45.980 --> 00:18:48.990 align:middle line:84%
They keep the wife, they keep
the car, they keep the money,

00:18:48.990 --> 00:18:52.460 align:middle line:84%
they keep the job, but
they're empty inside

00:18:52.460 --> 00:18:53.720 align:middle line:90%
and nothing has any meaning.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:56.690 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, and if we--

00:18:56.690 --> 00:18:59.720 align:middle line:84%
and this is a very subtle,
it's a very powerful concept--

00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:02.390 align:middle line:84%
if we go through
the world feeling

00:19:02.390 --> 00:19:06.680 align:middle line:84%
that we must hold tight on
everything that we've ever

00:19:06.680 --> 00:19:09.650 align:middle line:84%
amassed in our lives, and that
we love, and that we hold dear,

00:19:09.650 --> 00:19:12.350 align:middle line:84%
that's creations
trigger and that's

00:19:12.350 --> 00:19:13.910 align:middle line:84%
the assurance that
we will lose them

00:19:13.910 --> 00:19:15.650 align:middle line:90%
