00:19:15.650 --> 00:19:18.590 align:middle line:84%
Rather than recognizing the
beauty and the gifts of all

00:19:18.590 --> 00:19:21.140 align:middle line:84%
that have ever come to
us, of our relationships,

00:19:21.140 --> 00:19:23.870 align:middle line:84%
